Class LeonardoMlService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.cloud.sdk.services.scp.machinelearning.LeonardoMlService
  • Deprecated. 
    This module will be discontinued, along with its classes and methods.

    @Beta
 @Deprecated
public class LeonardoMlService
extends Object
    A generic service accessor for Leonardo ML Services. Create with the methods of LeonardoMlFoundation.

    Be aware that this class is in Beta (as indicated by the annotation) and therefore subject to breaking changes.
